FuncDef:
The alarm drop-rate arp-vlan-car disable command disables the alarm function for ARP VLAN CAR.
The undo alarm drop-rate arp-vlan-car disable command enables the alarm function for ARP VLAN CAR.
By default, the alarm function is enabled for ARP VLAN CAR.
ExtraInfo:
Usage Scenario
To disable the alarm function for ARP VLAN CAR, run the alarm drop-rate arp-vlan-car disable command. To enable the alarm function for ARP VLAN CAR, run the undo alarm drop-rate arp-vlan-car disable command.
Precautions
In VS mode, this command is supported only by the admin VS.
